{
  "stem": "16930.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 298.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He never saw one before until he moved to Vienna, where he saw Jews from Poland who were pious Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that's where he got his ideas from, is straight from the Catholic church.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the guy who was captured by, and hanged in Israel, the-- the one-- the mass murderer--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eichmann went to the same school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had the same history teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where they got the ideas from, that Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were such Catholic schools all over the place, and other even Protestant schools, but not as bad as the Catholics.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where all these people had this inborn hatred against Jews already, ready for the Nazis to work on and utilize.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now this is being denied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we're 50 years down the road, and the world has not changed that much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The world has changed somewhat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I believe technically a Holocaust is still possible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm watching this stuff on television, what's going on-- and what's the town in Yugoslavia?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bosnia and Sarajevo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bosnia, Serbia, Bosnia, where they have cleansing, ethnic cleansing, where they kill people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They rape the women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They kill people, mass graves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's still going on today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And fortunately, the UN is having hearings about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These things are going on in Africa, one in Africa, where we were-- where we were there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Americans intervened about a year ago, in Burundi-- what's the town next to Burundi, that state there, where the Tutsis killed the Hutus, over a million were killed, two different tribes; in Somalia, where people are all the same, they part of the Arab League.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They speak the same language, have the same religion.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
